alphabetsoup.framework
Class Quadtree

java.lang.Object
  alphabetsoup.framework.Quadtree

public class Quadtree
extends java.lang.Object

Quadtree mantains a tree where each node quadrasects the area of its parent, used for fast lookup of local interactions between objects.

Author:
Chris Hazard
